msgid "You must pass a doctor profile ID"
msgstr "Du måste klara en läkarprofil ID"

#: public/d2g-connect-shortcodes.php:634
msgid "You need to provide us with information about your fields of study. "
msgstr "Du måste ge oss information om dina studieinriktningar."

#: public/d2g-connect-shortcodes.php:639
msgid ""
"You need to provide us with information about your the languages that you "
"speak. "
msgstr "Du måste förse oss med information om de språk du talar."

#: public/template-functions.php:569
msgid ""
"Your account data is not complete yet. So we need your first name and last "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Dina kontouppgifter är inte fullständiga ännu. Vi behöver därför ditt "
"förnamn och efternamn."

#: public/template-functions.php:629
msgid ""
"Your anonymous booking was successful! If you would like to be able to "
"manage your booking later on, we advise you to create an account."
msgstr ""
"Din anonyma bokning var framgångsrik! Om du vill kunna hantera din bokning "
"senare rekommenderar vi att du skapar ett konto."

#: public/template-functions.php:632
msgid ""
"Your booking and creation of your user was successful. Before you can login "
"to manage your booking on the \"my appointments page\" in your dashboard, "
"you will first have to activate the account by clicking on the link in the "
"email that we have send you."
msgstr ""
"Din bokning och skapandet av din användare var framgångsrik. Innan du kan "
"logga in för att hantera din bokning på sidan \"mina möten\" i din "
"instrumentpanel måste du först aktivera kontot genom att klicka på länken i "
"det e-postmeddelande som vi har skickat till dig."

#: public/template-functions.php:627
msgid ""
"Your booking was successful. You can now manage your booking on the \"my "
"appointments page\" in your dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Din bokning var framgångsrik. Du kan nu hantera din bokning på sidan \"Mina "
"möten\" i din instrumentpanel."

